<item>
            <title>[LU-4813] LFSCK orphan iteration should NOT use new portal to easy UT work in the future</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4813</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, LFSCK orphan iteration uses OST_IDX_PORTAL which is a new portal special for LFSCK since lustre-2.6. In fact, we can reuse the OUT_PROTAL for the same purpose and simplify UT work in the future.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This fixing should be done before Lustre-2.6 release, otherwise it will cause interoperability issues.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
